---
title: Korean Inspired Glazed Lamb Koftas with Smacked Cucumber and Jasmine Rice
description: Koftas (also known as 'kofte') are a popular type of meatball style dish. These Korean Inspired Glazed Lamb Koftas use the popular Korean condiment gochujang for a savoury-sweet flavour and are perfect for a balanced lifestyle.
